<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Escalation: ${formTitle} pending > 5 days</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body, table, td, p { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; }
      img { border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
      table { border-collapse: collapse; }
      .email-wrapper { width: 100%; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 0; }
      .email-container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
      .header { background-color: #004aad; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
      .content { padding: 25px; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .content h2 { color: #004aad; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .details { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; }
      .details td { padding: 8px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; vertical-align: top; }
      .details .label { font-weight: bold; color: #555555; width: 35%; }
      .btn { background-color: #004aad; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 18px; display: inline-block; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 15px; }
      .footer { background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #555555; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.4; }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .content { padding: 15px; }
        .header { font-size: 18px; }
        .btn { display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body style="background-color: #f8f9fa; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <center class="email-wrapper">
      <table role="presentation" class="email-container">
        <tr>
          <td class="header">
            Escalation: Request Pending Action > 5 days
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class="content">
            <p>Dear {{hcdName}},</p>

            <p>
              The request <strong>{{formTitle}}</strong> submitted by <strong>{{requestorName}} (Staff ID: {{requestorStaffId}})</strong> has not been resolved by <strong>{{previousApproverName}}</strong> within 5 days.
            </p>

            <h2>Request Details</h2>

            <table class="details" role="presentation">
              <tr>
                <td class="label">Request Title:</td>
                <td>{{formTitle}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="label">Submitted By:</td>
                <td>{{requestorName}} ({{requestorStaffId}})</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="label">Department:</td>
                <td>{{department}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="label">Submission Date:</td>
                <td>{{submittedAt}}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="label">Pending Action By:</td>
                <td>{{previousApproverName}}</td>
              </tr>
            </table>

            <p>Please take the necessary action on this request:</p>

            <a href="{{approvalLink}}" class="btn">Review & Approve</a>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Thank you,<br />PHN Automation System</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class="footer">
            This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </center>
  </body>
</html>